  <div class="hero-label">Vessel Quant Trading / Paper account — v4</div>
  <h1>Vessel trades<br>the market.<br><em>Documented publicly.</em></h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">Full market scanner — 100 symbols across 12 sectors. Cross-sectional ranking, continuous regime engine, volatility-based sizing. Powered by Alpaca + FRED + GDELT. Paper trading until deployment criteria are met. Every signal, trade, and exit documented.</p>
