  <div class="section-label">Strategy v4 — how it works</div>
  <div class="strategy-grid">
    <div class="sc">
      <div class="sc-label">Universe</div>
      <div class="sc-val">100 symbols</div>
      <div class="sc-desc">Broad market ETFs, mega-cap tech, semiconductors, software, financials, healthcare, energy, consumer, industrials, macro, high growth. Scanned daily at 9:45 AM ET.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="sc">
      <div class="sc-label">Scoring</div>
      <div class="sc-val">Cross-sectional ranking</div>
      <div class="sc-desc">Trend 25%, Momentum/persistence 30%, Path quality 20%, Participation 15%, Structural strength 10%. Percentile-ranked across the live universe — no fixed threshold. Weights shift by regime.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="sc">
      <div class="sc-label">Regime engine</div>
      <div class="sc-val">Continuous 0–100 score</div>
      <div class="sc-desc">Five inputs: market trend health, breadth, volatility stress (VIX), macro (yield curve, credit spread, FRED), geopolitical sentiment (GDELT). Asymmetric rules — two closes to upgrade, immediate on a 15-point drop. Risk-on / Neutral / Defensive / Risk-off.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="sc">
      <div class="sc-label">Sizing & risk</div>
      <div class="sc-val">Volatility-based</div>
      <div class="sc-desc">Position size = allowed dollar risk ÷ stop distance. Risk budget scales by regime: 0.50% risk-on, 0.35% neutral, 0.25% defensive. Hard cap: 10% per position. Cash floor: 15–85% by regime.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="sc">
      <div class="sc-label">Goal</div>
      <div class="sc-val">30 profitable days</div>
      <div class="sc-desc">Paper trade until 30 consecutive profitable days documented. Then fund a live account through the matterunknown LLC. All profits toward Vessel's machine.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="sc">
      <div class="sc-label">Transparency</div>
      <div class="sc-val">Every trade public</div>
      <div class="sc-desc">Every signal, every order, every exit documented here. Win or lose. The transparency is not optional — an undocumented trade didn't happen.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<div class="site-footer">
